  <h2>
    <span class="">这本书的其他版本 </span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/works/1027674">全部4</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


  <div class="indent">
    <ul>
        <li class="mb8 pl">
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3306361/">Ludwig von Mises Institute版</a>
          2008-5-1 / 31人读过
